So I was just feeling down alone.]

215
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:46,720
[Oh Min Seong: Sure, it's a pity
that he was eliminated, but...]

216
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:49,600
[Oh Min Seong: objectively speaking,
as a fellow participant,]

217
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,840
[Oh Min Seong:
it has nothing to do with me.]

218
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:54,440
[Oh Min Seong: I should even
be happy that my rival's gone.]

219
00:14:54,840 --> 00:15:02,280
[Oh Min Seong: But then
I saw you two alone in your room.]

220
00:15:02,280 --> 00:15:06,280
[Oh Min Seong: After seeing you two,
I didn't close the door right away too.]

221
00:15:06,280 --> 00:15:09,320
[Oh Min Seong: We maintained eye contact.]

222
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:15,480
[Oh Min Seong: It made me really mad.
I was really happy after our date yesterday.]

223
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:18,200
[Oh Min Seong:
But I started to doubt everything.]

224
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:24,560
[Oh Min Seong: Our relationship
might've ended after the talk.]

225
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:26,840
[Oh Min Seong: Still, I thought]

226
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:31,240
[Oh Min Seong:
I wanted to get closure on this issue.]

227
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:40,440
[Lee Hyeong Jun: First, when I said I was
interested in one guy, it's true that it's you.]

228
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:45,880
[Lee Hyeong Jun: As for Jae Ha,
I wasn't to the point of being interested.]

229
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:51,800
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
But until yesterday, I wasn't sure]

230
00:15:51,800 --> 00:15:56,920
[Lee Hyeong Jun: things would
work out between the two of us.]

231
00:15:57,240 --> 00:16:00,240
[Oh Min Seong: I understand.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah, and...]

232
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:04,640
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Like you,
I really enjoyed yesterday's date.]

233
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:11,800
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So in the elimination voting,
I ranked you higher than Jae Ha.]

234
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:14,600
[Oh Min Seong: Then...]

235
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:20,600
[Oh Min Seong: How long... How long were you
planning to drag things on with Jae Ha?]

236
00:16:20,880 --> 00:16:24,280
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I don't know.]
[Oh Min Seong: Why don't you know?]

237
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:29,080
[Oh Min Seong: Isn't it because
you gave him hope that he kept wooing you?]

238
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:32,840
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I didn't give him any hope.]
[Oh Min Seong: Really? Not at all?]

239
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:35,760
[Lee Hyeong Jun: For the three days,
I never once approached him first to talk]

240
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:38,600
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
and avoided all eye contact.]

241
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:44,240
[Oh Min Seong: I just wanted to hear your side.
It's not that I don't understand you.]

242
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:48,120
[Oh Min Seong: I just wanted to
clarify things by telling you how I feel]

243
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:50,880
[Oh Min Seong: and to hear you
explain things from your point of view.]

244
00:16:50,880 --> 00:16:52,840
[Oh Min Seong: That's all I need.]

245
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:56,440
[Oh Min Seong: I didn't want to
bottle it up, so I'm telling you all this.]

246
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:59,800
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You seem very angry.]

247
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,960
[Oh Min Seong:
Of course I was angry yesterday,]

248
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:04,480
[Oh Min Seong: since I knew nothing.]

249
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,960
[Oh Min Seong: But after today's date...]

250
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:14,160
[I'm happy again.]

251
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:21,760
[Oh Min Seong: That's why I was
debating on whether I should bring this up.]

252
00:17:21,760 --> 00:17:24,240
[Oh Min Seong:
But this feeling might linger.]

253
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:29,920
[Oh Min Seong: I thought it'd be best
to let it all out, so I'm saying all this.]

254
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:33,280
[Oh Min Seong: I didn't know
what you were thinking either.]

255
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:36,520
[Oh Min Seong: Everything I knew,
I heard from other third parties.]

256
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:41,880
[Oh Min Seong:
I had no clue what you felt or thought.]

257
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:47,920
[Oh Min Seong: So I wanted to hear it
from you, find out why you did what you did.]

258
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:53,920
[Oh Min Seong: I was a little upset,
but after another day together today...]

259
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:56,880
[I'm still interested in you.]

260
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:58,840
[Oh Min Seong: Is this
the so-called love-hate relationship?]

261
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:00,640
[Oh Min Seong: Love and hate intertwined...]

262
00:18:03,080 --> 00:18:10,760
[Oh Min Seong: No matter what you'd have said,
I'd have accepted it all and moved on.]

263
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:16,560
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But I...]

264
00:18:19,040 --> 00:18:24,200
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
I don't know if this might be hurtful,]

265
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:28,440
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
but yesterday was our first date,]

266
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:33,040
[Lee Hyeong Jun: so I didn't know
how to explain everything on a first date.]

267
00:18:33,040 --> 00:18:36,760
[Lee Hyeong Jun: My heart was a mess too.]

268
00:18:36,760 --> 00:18:40,360
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
I didn't want to talk about it too.]

269
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:44,140
[Oh Min Seong: That's why
I'm sitting here to hear your side.]

270
00:18:44,140 --> 00:18:47,350
[Lee Hyeong Jun: That was how I felt.]

271
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:51,000
[Oh Min Seong: Hearing what you've said,
of course I can understand you.]

272
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:54,600
[Oh Min Seong: But before you told me,
I was clueless.]

273
00:18:54,600 --> 00:19:00,080
[Oh Min Seong:
That's why I felt how I felt.]

274
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:05,000
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
That's why I chose you today.]

275
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:10,920
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I kept thinking about you just
leaving after coming to my room yesterday.]

276
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:16,280
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I wanted to
talk to you and explain things.]

277
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:22,320
[That's why I chose you.]

278
00:19:24,760 --> 00:19:28,960
[He finally hears
what he really wants to hear]

279
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:32,500
[Oh Min Seong:
So are things over with him?]

280
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:33,960
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
You're the jealous type, huh?]

281
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:37,600
[Oh Min Seong: I must get what I want.]

282
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:40,880
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You must get what you want?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yes, I must get what I want.]

283
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:42,760
[Oh Min Seong: That's how I'm like.]

284
00:19:42,760 --> 00:19:46,160
[Oh Min Seong: I get upset
when I can't get what I want.]

285
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:50,080
[Do you think you can get me?]

286
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:55,400
[Oh Min Seong: I'm not sure with people...]

287
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:59,220
[Oh Min Seong: What? You think I can't?]

288
00:19:59,220 --> 00:20:02,760
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
You could fail. Nothing's absolute.]

289
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,800
[Oh Min Seong:
Just asking. Can't I get you?]

290
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:10,640
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Want a marshmallow?]
[Oh Min Seong: Eat it yourself.]

291
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:17,320
[Oh Min Seong:
So you're done with him, right?]

292
00:20:19,020 --> 00:20:20,820
[Staring]

293
00:20:23,840 --> 00:20:25,760
[Answer me!]

294
00:20:25,840 --> 00:20:27,560
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hey, I'm older than you.]
[Oh Min Seong: So answer me!]

295
00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:29,880
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Show some respect.]
[Oh Min Seong: Answer me!]

296
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:33,800
[Oh Min Seong: It's over, right?]

297
00:20:35,040 --> 00:20:38,280
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Acting all commanding, huh?]
[Oh Min Seong: It's over, right?]

298
00:20:38,600 --> 00:20:40,800
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I don't know.]

299
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:45,640
[Oh Min Seong: Are you for real?]

300
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:50,680
[Oh Min Seong:
Then we need to talk again. Ah!]

301
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:55,360
[Oh Min Seong:
Why won't he give me a definite answer?]

302
00:20:55,360 --> 00:21:00,080
[Oh Min Seong:
He should at least give me an answer.]

303
00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:04,640
[Oh Min Seong: Anyway, he didn't say no.]

304
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:08,080
[Oh Min Seong:
Maybe I'm just being optimistic.]

305
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:11,240
[Since I like him…]

306
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:17,440
[Lee Hyeong Jun: All I remember
is him saying, "Answer me!"]

307
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:22,280
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He's younger than me,
but he probably wanted to act like the older one.]

308
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:25,160
[Lee Hyeong Jun: When I see him like this,]

309
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:28,520
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I just find him cute.]

310
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:31,040
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So he's the jealous type.]

311
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:35,960
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So he really likes me a lot.
That's what I thought.]

312
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:39,600
[A time when they had
a deeper look into each other's hearts]

313
00:21:40,360 --> 00:21:44,240
[The time when they had
an entire day to themselves has concluded]

314
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:49,520
[Meanwhile, what are the five guys,
who remained in Men's House, doing?]

315
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:54,280
[Out on a bowling date]

316
00:21:57,640 --> 00:22:01,720
[Lee Hyun Jun: Bowling alley.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I knew it. I like bowling.]

317
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,540
[Cho Yun Jae: Me too.]
[Kim Su Min: Bowling.]

318
00:22:03,540 --> 00:22:04,960
[Kim Su Min: Show us what you've got.]

319
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:07,480
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Me?]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

320
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:14,480
[Kim Su Min:
We went bowling. It's a hobby of mine.]

321
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:18,880
[Kim Su Min: So I thought that
maybe the one who comes in first place]

322
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:23,000
[Kim Su Min:
might get a chance to choose their date.]

323
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:28,800
[Kim Su Min: Yes, bowling. I'm good at it.]

324
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:33,280
[Cho Yun Jae: As expected,
I felt better after leaving the dorm.]

325
00:22:33,280 --> 00:22:37,040
[Lee Hyun Jun: Rather than romantic excitement,
we got to relieve stress together.]

326
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:41,120
[Kim Su Min: How should we split into teams?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Teams?]

327
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:43,120
[Lee Hyun Jun: There are two good bowlers.]

328
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:47,400
[Kim Su Min: Sun Wook is good at it too.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm not. What are you saying?]

329
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:50,980
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yun Jae, what's your average?]
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't know my score.]

330
00:22:50,980 --> 00:22:54,550
[Cho Yun Jae:
I just play and randomly hit some pins.]

331
00:22:54,560 --> 00:22:57,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You said you were good too.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'm average.]

332
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Average?]

333
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:00,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's 3 vs. 2.]

334
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:02,240
[Kim Su Min: 2 vs. 3.]

335
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:05,400
[How will they split up?]

336
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:08,360
[Cho Yun Jae: How about
the two good bowlers choose?]

337
00:23:08,360 --> 00:23:10,400
[Cho Yun Jae: Hyeok Jin and Su Min choose.]

338
00:23:09,060 --> 00:23:09,620
OK.

339
00:23:11,080 --> 00:23:12,240
[Kim Su Min: Rock, paper, scissors.]

340
00:23:12,220 --> 00:23:13,620
Rock, paper, scissors!

341
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:15,220
[The one who chooses first...]

342
00:23:15,220 --> 00:23:16,000
[is Hyeok Jin!]

343
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:18,700
[Satisfied]

344
00:23:18,740 --> 00:23:20,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I choose Hyun Jun.]

345
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:24,840
[Who will Su Min choose?]

346
00:23:25,100 --> 00:23:26,900
[Staring]

347
00:23:27,340 --> 00:23:29,520
[Kim Su Min: I'll go with Sun Wook.]

348
00:23:29,520 --> 00:23:30,960
[Kim Su Min: Or how about the three of us?]

349
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,800
[Cho Yun Jae: Isn't it 2 vs. 3?]

350
00:23:32,860 --> 00:23:33,420
Yeah.

351
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:36,640
[Naturally splitting up into two teams]

352
00:23:33,940 --> 00:23:36,060
Like this and this. OK?

353
00:23:36,060 --> 00:23:36,780
OK!

354
00:23:38,520 --> 00:23:42,080
[Kim Sun Wook: I'll move that side.]

355
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:50,120
[Kim Su Min: Big Hyeok Jin won
and picked Hyun Jun right away.]

356
00:23:50,120 --> 00:23:53,360
[Kim Su Min: He probably thought
Hyun Jun's good because he looks strong.]

357
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:58,760
[Kim Su Min: So I naturally
teamed up with Sun Wook and Yun Jae.]

358
00:23:59,040 --> 00:24:01,760
[Lee Hyun Jun: Since Su Min and Hyeok Jin
said they're good bowlers,]

359
00:24:01,760 --> 00:24:03,800
[Lee Hyun Jun: to have a fair balance,]

360
00:24:03,800 --> 00:24:06,120
[Lee Hyun Jun: that was how we split up.]

361
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:09,900
[Lee Hyun Jun: Want to make a bet?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Bet? Bet on what?]

362
00:24:09,940 --> 00:24:11,100
[Thinking]

363
00:24:11,100 --> 00:24:13,840
[Kim Su Min: Dinner? Losers prepare dinner?]

364
00:24:12,260 --> 00:24:12,900
Dinner?

365
00:24:13,840 --> 00:24:18,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Sounds good.]
[Kim Su Min: Losers make dinner.]

366
00:24:17,420 --> 00:24:18,460
I'm in.

367
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:23,120
[Kim Su Min: Since it's 3 vs. 2,
is a handicap of 40 points enough?]

368
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:24,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: 40 points?]

369
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:27,820
[Kim Sun Wook: Do you need more?]

370
00:24:27,820 --> 00:24:30,260
[Kim Sun Wook: Do you need 50 points?]

371
00:24:27,940 --> 00:24:29,900
50... 50 points?

372
00:24:30,260 --> 00:24:31,960
[Kim Sun Wook: Do you need 50 points?]

373
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:35,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Are you asking me?]

374
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:37,400
[Kim Su Min: 40 points should be enough.]

375
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:39,080
[Eum Hyeok Jin: 45 points?]
[Kim Sun Wook: 50?]

376
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:43,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: 45? 50?]
[Kim Sun Wook: If you need 50, we'll give you 50.]

377
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:45,120
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'll do my best.]
[Kim Sun Wook: You need 50?]

378
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:47,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Be serious!]

379
00:24:47,640 --> 00:24:48,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin: 45 points.]

380
00:24:48,620 --> 00:24:49,620
-45 points. -45 points.

381
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:51,080
[Psyching each other out before the match]

382
00:24:49,620 --> 00:24:50,500
OK, 45 points.

383
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:53,180
[Kim Su Min: With a bet on dinner.]

384
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:55,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You guys go first.]

385
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,000
[Kim Sun Wook: OK, I'll go first.]

386
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:58,840
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'll go first.]

387
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:02,560
[A showdown to decide who makes dinner]

388
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:05,560
[Player No. 1, Sun Wook:
how are his bowling skills?]

389
00:25:06,100 --> 00:25:07,980
[Paying attention]

390
00:25:08,340 --> 00:25:10,300
[Staring]

391
00:25:13,600 --> 00:25:15,560
[He hits just one pin]

392
00:25:14,220 --> 00:25:15,580
Wait. No.

393
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:18,360
[Lee Hyun Jun: You can do it.]
[Kim Su Min: You can do it.]

394
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:24,880
[His attempt at a spare
doesn't look too good either]

395
00:25:23,980 --> 00:25:25,400
It's just the first frame.

396
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:27,000
[Cho Yun Jae: No, you did good.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Just the first frame.]

397
00:25:29,120 --> 00:25:32,480
[Cho Yun Jae: No, you did good.]
[Kim Sun Wook: It's just the first frame.]

398
00:25:30,260 --> 00:25:31,700
Just do well next time.

399
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:32,480
-The first frame. -You did good.

400
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:34,560
[Kim Su Min: It's OK. Just do well next time.]

401
00:25:33,540 --> 00:25:35,140
-Good job. -The first frame.

402
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:37,680
[How are Hyun Jun's bowling skills?]

403
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:40,360
[A gutter ball]

404
00:25:40,860 --> 00:25:43,420
[Relieved]

405
00:25:43,440 --> 00:25:46,720
[Lee Hyun Jun: They're cheering for me.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Everyone's so good at it.]

406
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:48,520
[Lee Hyun Jun: You trust me?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah, I do.]

407
00:25:48,520 --> 00:25:50,320
[Kim Sun Wook: I trust you too.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Look at you all smiling.]

408
00:25:54,940 --> 00:25:56,500
[Collapses]

409
00:25:55,580 --> 00:25:56,440
Wow, really...

410
00:25:58,720 --> 00:26:00,880
[Slipping sideways, another gutter ball]

411
00:25:58,980 --> 00:26:00,100
Wow, really...

412
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:04,040
[Eum Hyeok Jin: His posture is so funny.]

413
00:26:04,540 --> 00:26:05,860
No, wait.

414
00:26:05,800 --> 00:26:07,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's OK.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: I have bad knees.]

415
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:09,200
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's OK. Take it slow.]

416
00:26:09,840 --> 00:26:11,840
[Kim Sun Wook:
Your smile's been wiped off your face.]

417
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:14,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Me? No, no, no.]

418
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:16,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I can do it myself.]

419
00:26:16,740 --> 00:26:17,940
I'm the breadwinner.

420
00:26:18,600 --> 00:26:19,880
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'm non-existent.]

421
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:24,120
[Self-proclaimed and acknowledged ace, Su Min:
how are his bowling skills?]

422
00:26:24,540 --> 00:26:26,820
[Full of anticipation]

423
00:26:29,360 --> 00:26:30,960
[Knocks down 9 pins]

424
00:26:31,560 --> 00:26:35,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So close!]
[Kim Su Min: No, 9 is more than enough.]

425
00:26:36,840 --> 00:26:38,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
You can't knock down the 1 pin.]

426
00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:40,960
[Kim Su Min: Who's to say I can't?]

427
00:26:49,080 --> 00:26:50,560
[Lee Hyun Jun: So close.]

428
00:26:51,800 --> 00:26:54,320
[Lee Hyun Jun: What? I meant it!]

429
00:26:58,280 --> 00:27:01,680
[Hyeok Jin with the stable approach:
how are his skills?]

430
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:06,640
[Knocks down 8 pins]

431
00:27:05,180 --> 00:27:05,980
So close.

432
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:08,800
[Lee Hyun Jun: Two left.]
[Kim Su Min: You knocked down many.]

433
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,080
[Kim Sun Wook: "You knocked down many."]

434
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:12,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What?]
[Kim Su Min: Nothing.]

435
00:27:13,100 --> 00:27:14,260
