how are his skills?]

437
00:27:14,260 --> 00:27:15,620
It was all just luck.

438
00:27:19,820 --> 00:27:21,480
-No sound! -Where's the thud?

439
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:25,100
[With a unique approach]

440
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:27,340
[Knocks down 7 pins]

441
00:27:25,500 --> 00:27:26,180
Nice.

442
00:27:26,180 --> 00:27:27,460
What was that?

443
00:27:27,980 --> 00:27:29,680
[Lee Hyun Jun: How did you do that?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: How did you do that?]

444
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:32,360
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't know either.]

445
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:36,760
[Kim Su Min: We must win today.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yes. I made dinner yesterday.]

446
00:27:36,760 --> 00:27:42,240
[Kim Su Min: Can you still cook dinner today?]
[Kim Sun Wook: What?]

447
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:45,920
[Kim Su Min: You look tired.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I can do it.]

448
00:27:47,280 --> 00:27:49,760
[Yun Jae throws the ball again]

449
00:27:47,420 --> 00:27:48,180
The sound...

450
00:27:50,580 --> 00:27:52,020
It's the right direction.

451
00:27:50,600 --> 00:27:53,080
[Lee Hyun Jun: He throws the ball well.]

452
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:56,160
[Barely knocks down just 1 pin]

453
00:27:55,020 --> 00:27:55,860
Nice.

454
00:27:56,200 --> 00:28:00,080
[Cho Yun Jae: What a pity. Really.]

455
00:28:03,840 --> 00:28:09,120
[Energizing time
after all the emotional turmoil]

456
00:28:06,740 --> 00:28:07,540
Nice.

457
00:28:09,940 --> 00:28:10,860
That's not good.

458
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:15,320
[But the level of enjoyment and skills
are separate matters]

459
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:13,340
I think he threw it wrong.

460
00:28:14,860 --> 00:28:15,540
So cute.

461
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:18,800
[Kim Su Min: Don't give up.]

462
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:23,140
[Full power]

463
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:28,680
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What?
You just knocked them down with brute force.]

464
00:28:31,300 --> 00:28:32,660
With brute force.

465
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:37,200
[Hyeok Jin's team's attack continues]

466
00:28:37,860 --> 00:28:38,660
Awesome.

467
00:28:38,800 --> 00:28:40,280
[Strike]

468
00:28:40,280 --> 00:28:42,080
[Cho Yun Jae: He's so good.]
[Kim Su Min: So good.]

469
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:49,160
[Another strike]

470
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:48,940
You're really good.

471
00:28:51,540 --> 00:28:53,180
It was really good this time.

472
00:28:54,120 --> 00:28:57,440
[Hyun Jun contributes too,
widening the score gap]

473
00:28:54,420 --> 00:28:55,380
Nice!

474
00:28:57,520 --> 00:28:59,070
[Lee Hyun Jun: What's for dinner?]

475
00:28:59,070 --> 00:29:01,310
[Cho Yun Jae: He asked what's for dinner!]

476
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:04,360
[Kim Su Min: Dinner...]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Already accepting it, huh?]

477
00:29:04,360 --> 00:29:05,600
[Kim Sun Wook: Dinner...]
[Kim Su Min: No.]

478
00:29:05,600 --> 00:29:08,760
[Cho Yun Jae: It's OK. We'll just cook dinner.]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah!]

479
00:29:09,280 --> 00:29:12,660
[Eum Hyeok Jin: How about pasta?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Add coffee to the bet?]

480
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:16,200
[Eum Hyeok Jin: All of a sudden?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: On our way back.]

481
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:19,200
[Yun Jae tries to bridge the gap]

482
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:20,880
[Another gutter ball]

483
00:29:21,140 --> 00:29:22,180
What a pity.

484
00:29:21,840 --> 00:29:24,160
[Kim Sun Wook:
Should the two of us just stop playing?]

485
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:26,480
[Cho Yun Jae: Our lane is weird... No, I...]

486
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:29,320
[Cho Yun Jae:
I just wanted to play one game.]

487
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:32,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I think I can relax a bit now.]

488
00:29:32,720 --> 00:29:35,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I thought it'd be fun
since I like bowling.]

489
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:37,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I thought it'd be fun.]

490
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:41,200
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But when we started playing,
it was more fun than I expected.]

491
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:43,480
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It really relieved stress]

492
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:46,080
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and took my mind off things.]

493
00:29:46,080 --> 00:29:48,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Just focused on bowling. It was great.]

494
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:51,320
[Lee Hyun Jun: We all had fun bowling,]

495
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:55,320
[Lee Hyun Jun:
a time for everyone to unwind.]

496
00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:58,720
[Kim Sun Wook:
Hyun Jun and I were in different teams.]

497
00:29:58,720 --> 00:30:00,720
[Kim Sun Wook:
When I saw him joking with Hyeok Jin,]

498
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:04,520
[Kim Sun Wook: he looked so cute
when smiling. Seeing him like that]

499
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:06,280
[Kim Sun Wook: made me happy.]

500
00:30:06,280 --> 00:30:11,680
[Kim Sun Wook:
His genuine smiles were what got me.]

501
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:16,640
[Kim Su Min: You know how they'd
give you high fives when you bowl well?]

502
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:20,040
[Kim Su Min: Sometimes our hands touched.]

503
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:25,120
[Kim Su Min: Touching hands,
and then lingering sometimes.]

504
00:30:25,120 --> 00:30:28,440
[Kim Su Min: It was my first time
having physical contact with Sun Wook.]

505
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:31,360
[Kim Su Min: That was the most memorable.]

506
00:30:32,280 --> 00:30:35,120
[I got a little nervous…]

507
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:37,480
[Cho Yun Jae: The group date was fun.]

508
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:44,440
[Cho Yun Jae: Anyway, I got a chance
to do something with Hyun Jun.]

509
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:46,160
[Cho Yun Jae: So I was really happy.]

510
00:30:47,280 --> 00:30:49,100
[Cho Yun Jae: Do you remember
what meal kits we have?]

511
00:30:49,100 --> 00:30:50,440
[Kim Sun Wook: Nakgopsae!
(octopus, intestine, and shrimp stew)]

512
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:52,120
[Cho Yun Jae: Nakgopsae...
(octopus, intestine, and shrimp stew)]

513
00:30:53,720 --> 00:30:56,540
[The group date ends with
the defeat of Su Min's team]

514
00:30:56,540 --> 00:31:00,340
[His Man]

515
00:31:05,880 --> 00:31:09,640
[Kim Su Min: Where'd you go with my coffee?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Sorry, sorry.]

516
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,560
[Kim Su Min: Why are you sorry?]

517
00:31:11,560 --> 00:31:14,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I went to the convenience store.]
[Kim Su Min: Really?]

518
00:31:14,360 --> 00:31:16,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I had to get something.]

519
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,040
[Sweet Su Min]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Thank you.]

520
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:23,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: At least we had fun.]
[Kim Su Min: It was fun.]

521
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:27,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: We really just had fun.]

522
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:31,000
[Kim Su Min: Yeah, just had fun.]

523
00:31:31,600 --> 00:31:36,520
[Awkward silence]

524
00:31:38,580 --> 00:31:40,020
[Stomach rumbling]

525
00:31:40,020 --> 00:31:43,640
[Kim Su Min: My stomach is starting again.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Same with me.]

526
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:47,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I got it from you.]
[Kim Su Min: But you really don't eat much.]

527
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I can't eat.]

528
00:31:50,520 --> 00:31:52,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Too much on my mind.]

529
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:55,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
It's a different kind of stress this time.]

530
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:58,680
[Kim Su Min: Care to elaborate?]

531
00:31:58,680 --> 00:32:00,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's been four days.]

532
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:02,760
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Other than this group date,]

533
00:32:02,760 --> 00:32:04,480
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I haven't been on a single date.]

534
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:08,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
The timing and all the choices I made...]

535
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:13,080
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Feels like
I've been denied with everything.]

536
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:16,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Since I came here...
It wasn't like this the last shoot,]

537
00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:19,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but I've been
having a lot of bad thoughts lately,]

538
00:32:20,840 --> 00:32:23,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: unlike before.]

539
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:27,000
[Hyeok Jin is spiraling and feels stuck]

540
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:31,440
[Kim Su Min:
I think I've become colder towards you]

541
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:33,760
[Kim Su Min: after the last shoot.]

542
00:32:34,360 --> 00:32:40,760
[Kim Su Min:
Sometimes I feel really guilty.]

543
00:32:42,280 --> 00:32:47,240
[Kim Su Min: We did talk a lot privately.]

544
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:51,520
[Kim Su Min: But then I suddenly
became so cold towards you.]

545
00:32:51,520 --> 00:32:53,840
[Kim Su Min: I thought it might be hurtful,]

546
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:59,160
[Kim Su Min: that you might be hurt by it.]

547
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:05,840
[Kim Su Min: Although I've said it, I...]

548
00:33:05,840 --> 00:33:09,600
[Kim Su Min:
I've been a little cautious, or...]

549
00:33:09,600 --> 00:33:16,320
[Kim Su Min: I did keep my distance from you.
I'm sorry about that.]

550
00:33:17,120 --> 00:33:20,440
[Kim Su Min:
I also sorta felt that you were a bit]

551
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:24,520
[Kim Su Min:
uneasy and awkward around me.]

552
00:33:24,520 --> 00:33:28,480
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Rather than feeling uneasy or awkward,]

553
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:32,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I just felt a huge wall between us.]

554
00:33:32,520 --> 00:33:37,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I couldn't even
think about approaching you.]

555
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:41,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Since I felt you
distancing yourself from me.]

556
00:33:41,360 --> 00:33:43,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I was fine with everything else,]

557
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:46,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but, um...]

558
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:53,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: There was a moment
when I wondered if you had to go this far]

559
00:33:53,120 --> 00:33:54,760
[Eum Hyeok Jin: since I got here.]

560
00:33:56,280 --> 00:33:58,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: In the beginning,
when we came to this dorm,]

561
00:33:58,960 --> 00:34:04,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: while we were waiting
at the stairs, I was right in the back.]

562
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:07,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was wondering
why you turned your back on me.]

563
00:34:07,600 --> 00:34:09,040
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's what I felt.]

564
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:13,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Everyone was chatting together,]

565
00:34:13,560 --> 00:34:16,760
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and I was talking,
but I felt like you were]

566
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:20,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: completely ignoring me,
so I was really confused.]

567
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:24,199
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I wondered
why you had to go this far.]

568
00:34:24,199 --> 00:34:28,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Were you worried
that I might try to woo you again?]

569
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:31,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Is that why you're
keeping your distance right off the bat?]

570
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:35,199
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's what I thought.]

571
00:34:37,040 --> 00:34:40,480
[Kim Su Min: I think
I overcomplicated things in my head]

572
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:43,639
[Kim Su Min: and felt uncomfortable.]

573
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:48,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'd be lying if I said]

574
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:50,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: it didn't bother me at all.]

575
00:34:53,080 --> 00:34:58,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
To be honest, I do feel a little hurt.]

576
00:34:58,520 --> 00:35:01,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I couldn't help but notice]

577
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:06,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin: how different you are
as compared to the last shoot.]

578
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:10,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: In the last shoot,
I went to your room a lot.]

579
00:35:10,120 --> 00:35:13,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Although that room itself was sorta]

580
00:35:13,280 --> 00:35:16,040
[Eum Hyeok Jin: where everyone gathered.]

581
00:35:16,040 --> 00:35:19,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
In this shoot, you also very naturally]

582
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:22,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
borrowed Sun Wook's clothes and stuff.]

583
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:25,480
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I just felt a bit upset.]

584
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:29,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
When I expressed my interest in you,]

585
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:31,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: if only you had treated me]

586
00:35:31,960 --> 00:35:33,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: in a similar way.]

587
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:37,800
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Why didn't you treat me like that?]

588
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:40,080
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was just sad about that.]

589
00:35:40,080 --> 00:35:43,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But it's all in the past.]

590
00:35:43,120 --> 00:35:46,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's just how I've felt.]

591
00:35:51,680 --> 00:35:55,600
[Kim Su Min: So who do you like now?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why do you ask?]

592
00:35:55,600 --> 00:35:58,160
[Kim Su Min: I can kinda tell,]

593
00:35:58,160 --> 00:36:00,800
[Kim Su Min: but I'm not sure.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Who do you think it is?]

594
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:04,120
[Kim Su Min: Han Gyeol?]

595
00:36:08,560 --> 00:36:13,800
[Kim Su Min: My intuition is not bad.]

596
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:17,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I didn't expect
to talk about this with you.]

597
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:22,440
[Kim Su Min: Yeah, we ended up alone here.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I know.]

598
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:26,960
[Kim Su Min: In the last shoot, Hyeok Jin
proactively showed his interest in me.]

599
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:32,880
[Kim Su Min: After I rejected him,
I just felt really uneasy around him.]

600
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:36,520
[Kim Su Min:
So I distanced myself from him.]

601
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:39,480
[Kim Su Min: I feel so sorry,
knowing that he was really hurt by it.]

602
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:41,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Su Min brought it up with me today.]

603
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:47,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He said I might feel hurt,]

604
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:52,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but he brought up the matter
about him ignoring me]

605
00:36:52,600 --> 00:36:54,200
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and excluding me.]

606
00:36:54,560 --> 00:36:57,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I'm grateful that he brought it up first.]

607
00:36:59,560 --> 00:37:03,560
[The two had a candid and honest
heart-to-heart talk]

608
00:37:00,820 --> 00:37:02,820
Will our rooming situation change?

609
00:37:03,560 --> 00:37:06,360
[Kim Su Min:
Will I have to stay in Block C alone?]

610
00:37:06,560 --> 00:37:09,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't think
they'll make you stay alone.]

611
00:37:09,600 --> 00:37:13,920
[Kim Su Min:
I'm fine with staying there alone.]

612
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:17,680
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Can I drive you out
all the time and have chats there?]

613
00:37:17,680 --> 00:37:21,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin: "Can you leave for a bit?"]
[Kim Su Min: Um...]

614
00:37:21,160 --> 00:37:25,320
[Kim Su Min: I'd appreciate it
