617
00:37:32,440 --> 00:37:35,280
[Kim Su Min: I'll go to Block B then.]

618
00:37:35,280 --> 00:37:38,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Make a plan.
I'll arrange the schedule for you.]

619
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:40,560
[Kim Su Min: Get approval first.]

620
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:44,520
[Kim Sun Wook: Why does no one clean up?]

621
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:48,120
[Kim Sun Wook: No one cleans up.]

622
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:55,320
[Kim Sun Wook: Gosh, Lee Hyeong Jun!
Lee Hyeong Jun!]

623
00:37:55,440 --> 00:37:58,760
[Sun Wook tidies up the room
while his roommates are out]

624
00:37:56,980 --> 00:37:58,180
Lee Hyeong Jun!

625
00:37:58,740 --> 00:38:00,740
Lee Hyeong Jun never cleans up.

626
00:38:09,240 --> 00:38:12,800
[Yun Jae is deep in thought]

627
00:38:16,260 --> 00:38:19,340
[Snooping]

628
00:38:21,260 --> 00:38:24,020
[A glance]

629
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:30,040
