630
00:38:37,060 --> 00:38:38,220
[Hi.]

631
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:39,720
[Lee Hyun Jun:
What are you doing? Playing chess?]

632
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:43,400
[Cho Yun Jae:
No, I just saw the chess board around.]

633
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:49,480
[Lee Hyun Jun:
The pieces are in weird positions.]

634
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:55,160
[Lee Hyun Jun: You know how to play chess?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yes, I learned, but I forgot.]

635
00:38:56,720 --> 00:38:59,200
[Cho Yun Jae: How was it?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: How was what?]

636
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:01,840
[Cho Yun Jae: Just. Your dates.]

637
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:06,040
[Lee Hyun Jun: My dates?
The dates themselves were fun.]

638
00:39:06,040 --> 00:39:09,220
[Cho Yun Jae: Really?]

639
00:39:09,220 --> 00:39:10,340
[Lee Hyun Jun: What about you?]

640
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:15,580
[Cho Yun Jae: Me? To be honest,]

641
00:39:15,580 --> 00:39:18,320
[Cho Yun Jae: I have yet to go on a date]

642
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:20,960
[Cho Yun Jae: where my heart was in it.]

643
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:25,240
[Cho Yun Jae: As I've always said,]

644
00:39:25,240 --> 00:39:30,200
[Cho Yun Jae: I always chose you, so...]

645
00:39:30,200 --> 00:39:32,360
[Cho Yun Jae: That's that.]

646
00:39:34,400 --> 00:39:36,520
[Lee Hyun Jun:
But we had no chance to go out on a date.]

647
00:39:36,520 --> 00:39:39,280
[Cho Yun Jae:
