00:53:01,760 --> 00:53:05,260
[Su Min's in charge of nakgopsae]
[Sun Wook's in charge of stone pot bulgogi (beef)]

857
00:53:05,640 --> 00:53:08,600
[Yun Jae's in charge of the instant rice]

858
00:53:06,780 --> 00:53:07,740
Just blanch it.

859
00:53:12,620 --> 00:53:14,940
[Kim Su Min: Can I take a photo of you?]

860
00:53:21,760 --> 00:53:25,960
[Lee Hyun Jun: Are you being punished?]
[Cho Yun Jae: No, well... It's similar.]

861
00:53:27,180 --> 00:53:28,260
[A glance]

862
00:53:33,900 --> 00:53:35,380
-Hi. -Hi.

863
00:53:36,880 --> 00:53:40,560
[Kim Su Min: Let's dig in.]
[OK.]

864
00:53:41,000 --> 00:53:44,840
[Lee Hyun Jun: Do you want a lot?]
[Taichi: I want more large intestines.]

865
00:53:45,480 --> 00:53:47,840
[Kim Su Min: He has a clear preference.]

866
00:53:46,060 --> 00:53:47,590
-Yeah. -Large intestines.

867
00:53:51,760 --> 00:53:55,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You're back. Have you eaten?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes, but I'm still hungry.]

868
00:53:56,120 --> 00:53:59,920
[Kim Han Gyeol: Is this seat taken?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Sit.]

869
00:54:00,260 --> 00:54:02,020
You're feeling hungry today?

870
00:54:03,180 --> 00:54:03,780
Finally.

871
00:54:03,780 --> 00:54:05,100
-Really, finally. -Finally.

872
00:54:05,100 --> 00:54:06,840
You really haven't been eating.

873
00:54:06,840 --> 00:54:12,240
[Kim Su Min: I heard you're good at bowling.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm not good. I just like it.]

874
00:54:08,460 --> 00:54:09,220
-Me? -Yeah.

875
00:54:16,400 --> 00:54:21,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why are you drinking so much
water? You'd be full just from the water.]

876
00:54:29,380 --> 00:54:32,100
[A glance]

877
00:54:36,960 --> 00:54:40,400
[Possibly out of discomfort,
Han Gyeol gets up first]

878
00:54:59,480 --> 00:55:01,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Thank you for the meal.]

879
00:55:12,080 --> 00:55:14,920
[Han Gyeol and Hyeok Jin
run into each other outside]

880
00:55:15,000 --> 00:55:17,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Come to my room later.
I have something for you.]

881
00:55:17,720 --> 00:55:19,640
[Kim Han Gyeol: Really?]

882
00:55:20,640 --> 00:55:21,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No, I'll go upstairs.]

883
00:55:21,720 --> 00:55:23,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Wait for me. I'll get it.]

884
00:55:23,920 --> 00:55:26,720
[Kim Han Gyeol: Go ahead.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yup.]

885
00:55:33,720 --> 00:55:36,280
[Hyeok Jin takes something out of the fridge]

886
00:55:38,520 --> 00:55:41,520
[Kim Su Min: Oh, he really bought it.]
[Cho Yun Jae: What?]

887
00:55:41,520 --> 00:55:42,760
[Kim Su Min: Nothing.]

888
00:55:42,760 --> 00:55:45,720
[Cho Yun Jae:
I want to know too. What is it?]

889
00:55:45,720 --> 00:55:49,240
[Kim Su Min: Just something.]

890
00:55:49,240 --> 00:55:51,680
[Cho Yun Jae: Wow, it's not easy.]

891
00:55:52,720 --> 00:55:54,840
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Quick, huh?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: So quick.]

892
00:55:54,840 --> 00:55:57,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm like Flash.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: What could it be?]

893
00:55:57,880 --> 00:56:01,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's nothing big.]

894
00:56:01,680 --> 00:56:04,960
[What did Hyeok Jin prepare for Han Gyeol?]

895
00:56:05,040 --> 00:56:08,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's so warm.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's starting to feel like home.]

896
00:56:09,480 --> 00:56:11,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: This is home.]

897
00:56:11,120 --> 00:56:13,520
[Kim Han Gyeol: It feels familiar now.]

898
00:56:13,020 --> 00:56:14,820
-Hmm? -It feels familiar now.

899
00:56:15,920 --> 00:56:18,240
[Ta-da]
[Kim Han Gyeol: What is it? Oh!]

900
00:56:18,240 --> 00:56:19,520
[Kim Han Gyeol: My nickname!]

901
00:56:19,920 --> 00:56:24,960
[Han Gyeol is all smiles
after seeing Hyeok Jin's gift]

902
00:56:20,000 --> 00:56:21,660
There wasn't any B.B.BIG ice cream.

903
00:56:21,660 --> 00:56:22,740
Really?

904
00:56:22,740 --> 00:56:24,380
So I bought Melona ice cream.

905
00:56:25,360 --> 00:56:28,480
[3 hours ago]

906
00:56:29,520 --> 00:56:31,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
On our way back from bowling,]

907
00:56:31,240 --> 00:56:34,040
[Eum Hyeok Jin: we stopped to get coffee.]

908
00:56:34,040 --> 00:56:36,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: There was
an ice cream shop next to it.]

909
00:56:36,320 --> 00:56:37,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
An unmanned ice cream shop.]

910
00:56:37,640 --> 00:56:39,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: And I suddenly
thought of Melona ice cream,]

911
00:56:39,560 --> 00:56:43,080
[Eum Hyeok Jin: so I thought
I should buy it. Bought it on a whim.]

912
00:56:48,720 --> 00:56:51,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I just suddenly wanted to buy some Melona.]

913
00:56:51,600 --> 00:56:53,240
[Kim Han Gyeol: Really?]

914
00:56:52,500 --> 00:56:53,060
Yeah.

915
00:56:54,200 --> 00:56:57,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I said I was craving Melona.]

916
00:56:57,680 --> 00:57:00,040
[Kim Han Gyeol: I woke up from a deep sleep
after drinking.]

917
00:57:00,040 --> 00:57:01,880
[Kim Han Gyeol:
It's nice having ice cream now.]

918
00:57:02,240 --> 00:57:06,880
[Kim Han Gyeol: You know what I mean, right?
It's so refreshing.]

919
00:57:06,880 --> 00:57:09,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It must've been nice
taking a walk while looking out at the sea.]

920
00:57:10,840 --> 00:57:12,800
[Kim Han Gyeol: It was therapeutic.]

921
00:57:14,920 --> 00:57:16,200
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Can I ask how it went?]

922
00:57:16,340 --> 00:57:16,980
Hmm?

923
00:57:16,920 --> 00:57:18,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Can I ask
how you sorted out the relationship?]

924
00:57:18,720 --> 00:57:20,960
[Kim Han Gyeol: That's a secret.]

925
00:57:20,960 --> 00:57:24,040
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I should keep some secrets too.]

926
00:57:24,040 --> 00:57:26,240
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I'm too much of an open book here.]

927
00:57:26,240 --> 00:57:28,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Is that so?]

928
00:57:28,720 --> 00:57:30,800
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
When can we have a conversation]

929
00:57:30,800 --> 00:57:33,040
[Eum Hyeok Jin: outside the dorm?]

930
00:57:33,040 --> 00:57:34,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I think about that a lot.]

931
00:57:34,720 --> 00:57:38,240
[Kim Han Gyeol: I honestly want to
spend time outside with you, if possible.]

932
00:57:38,240 --> 00:57:42,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's crazy
how impossible it's been so far.]

933
00:57:45,000 --> 00:57:46,800
[Kim Han Gyeol: How many
relationships have you been in?]

934
00:57:46,800 --> 00:57:47,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Relationships?]

935
00:57:47,960 --> 00:57:51,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Two relationships
since I came of age.]

936
00:57:51,120 --> 00:57:54,240
[Kim Han Gyeol: You are so careful.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's not it.]

937
00:57:54,240 --> 00:57:56,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: As I've said,]

938
00:57:56,000 --> 00:57:58,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I chose my career over love.]

939
00:57:58,960 --> 00:58:05,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But during that time,
I naturally just got into relationships.]

940
00:58:05,640 --> 00:58:09,040
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I'm not very experienced, so I...]

941
00:58:09,040 --> 00:58:11,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: When you asked me
about my ultimate flirting moves,]

942
00:58:11,560 --> 00:58:13,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I wasn't sure either.]

943
00:58:13,400 --> 00:58:15,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I just tried to be honest.]

944
00:58:15,960 --> 00:58:18,300
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Tough on the outside, soft on the inside.]

945
00:58:18,300 --> 00:58:19,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah, you're right.]

946
00:58:19,560 --> 00:58:22,080
[Kim Han Gyeol: A perfect example of that.]

947
00:58:22,080 --> 00:58:24,680
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I tend to...]

948
00:58:24,680 --> 00:58:26,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I worry a lot]

949
00:58:26,640 --> 00:58:28,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: about what might irk them.]

950
00:58:28,920 --> 00:58:29,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Stuff like,]

951
00:58:29,960 --> 00:58:32,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
"Will he dislike it if I do this for him?"]

952
00:58:32,440 --> 00:58:34,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I'm always having these thoughts.]

953
00:58:34,400 --> 00:58:36,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I'm more cautious.]

954
00:58:40,680 --> 00:58:44,160
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I thought about it at the beach today.]

955
00:58:50,040 --> 00:58:54,800
[Kim Han Gyeol: I suddenly
want to get to know you better.]

956
00:59:01,640 --> 00:59:03,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That makes me so happy.]

957
00:59:03,960 --> 00:59:05,800
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What made you think that?]

958
00:59:07,640 --> 00:59:12,600
[You're so warm.]

959
00:59:15,320 --> 00:59:17,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
It's like my stock is rising.]

960
00:59:17,400 --> 00:59:21,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Rather than ups and downs,
it's more like a consistent upward trend.]

961
00:59:22,840 --> 00:59:26,200
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Did my ultimate flirting moves work?]

962
00:59:26,200 --> 00:59:30,280
[Kim Han Gyeol: By my standards,
this is your ultimate flirting move.]

963
00:59:31,280 --> 00:59:34,200
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's the little things]

964
00:59:34,200 --> 00:59:36,160
[Kim Han Gyeol: that really get to me.]

965
00:59:36,160 --> 00:59:41,960
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I don't think I'm very good at stuff like]

966
00:59:41,960 --> 00:59:45,040
[Kim Han Gyeol:
gift-giving or expressing my feelings.]

967
00:59:45,040 --> 00:59:48,440
[Kim Han Gyeol: In some sense, I'm
quite clumsy when it comes to relationships.]

968
00:59:48,960 --> 00:59:51,240
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Feels like you're the opposite of me.]

969
00:59:51,240 --> 00:59:54,240
[Kim Han Gyeol:
You're meticulous and considerate.]

970
00:59:54,240 --> 00:59:57,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
It applies to people I care about, I guess?]

971
00:59:57,280 --> 01:00:01,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I'm not used to and not the best at]

972
01:00:01,160 --> 01:00:06,200
[Eum Hyeok Jin: expressing my true feelings,
so I tend to whine about it]

973
01:00:06,200 --> 01:00:08,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and joke around a lot.]

974
01:00:08,400 --> 01:00:13,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I think
that's how I care for my loved ones.]

975
01:00:13,320 --> 01:00:16,720
[Kim Han Gyeol: I thought of this too,]

976
01:00:16,720 --> 01:00:20,200
[Kim Han Gyeol:
that going to the beach with you]

977
01:00:20,200 --> 01:00:23,240
[Kim Han Gyeol: would've been fun too.]

978
01:00:23,240 --> 01:00:24,680
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It sounds fun.]

979
01:00:24,680 --> 01:00:28,760
[Kim Han Gyeol: I had that thought too.]

980
01:00:28,760 --> 01:00:30,280
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's why today,]

981
01:00:30,280 --> 01:00:35,680
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I rushed to get ready]

982
01:00:35,680 --> 01:00:36,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and came here.]

983
01:00:36,920 --> 01:00:39,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: In my own way, I wanted to]

984
01:00:39,880 --> 01:00:41,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: see what you'd wear today.]

985
01:00:41,920 --> 01:00:43,720
[Kim Han Gyeol: I see.]

986
01:00:45,360 --> 01:00:50,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
So I took out my last black coat,]

987
01:00:50,000 --> 01:00:51,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but it ended up like this.]

988
01:00:55,920 --> 01:00:59,020
[Kim Han Gyeol: From now on,
I want to go on a date with you.]

989
01:00:59,020 --> 01:01:00,760
[Kim Han Gyeol: Before it's too late.]

990
01:00:59,020 --> 01:01:00,460
Tomorrow...

991
01:01:00,760 --> 01:01:04,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I also want to go on a date tomorrow.]

992
01:01:04,880 --> 01:01:07,400
[Kim Han Gyeol:
We have to go on one date, at least.]

993
01:01:07,400 --> 01:01:09,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Just once?]

994
01:01:11,120 --> 01:01:13,440
[Kim Han Gyeol: As many as possible.]

995
01:01:16,640 --> 01:01:19,840
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I don't know. I'm getting shy.]

996
01:01:19,840 --> 01:01:22,000
[Kim Han Gyeol: What's with you?]

997
01:01:22,000 --> 01:01:24,040
[Kim Han Gyeol:
You were good at being mushy yesterday.]

998
01:01:25,960 --> 01:01:28,040
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't do anything,]

999
01:01:28,040 --> 01:01:30,360
[Kim Han Gyeol:
but after Lee Hyeok Jin left,]

1000
01:01:30,360 --> 01:01:35,600
[Kim Han Gyeol: Eum Hyeok Jin has been
way more forward with his advances.]

1001
01:01:35,600 --> 01:01:38,480
[Kim Han Gyeol:
He's also been showing me more concern.]

1002
01:01:38,480 --> 01:01:41,680
[Kim Han Gyeol: He was always around me,
to the point that I'm aware of it.]

1003
01:01:41,680 --> 01:01:44,800
[Kim Han Gyeol:
He's been so directly... considerate?]

1004
01:01:44,800 --> 01:01:48,560
[Kim Han Gyeol: Expressive? Consideration?
I think it's my first time]

1005
01:01:48,560 --> 01:01:51,400
[Kim Han Gyeol:
being treated with such care.]

1006
01:01:51,880 --> 01:01:54,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Yes, the timing is quite questionable,]

1007
01:01:54,640 --> 01:01:57,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: him shifting his focus onto me
after he was rejected.]

1008
01:01:57,720 --> 01:02:01,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He could've already decided
and only told me now after he's sure.]

1009
01:02:01,320 --> 01:02:02,760
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Or he was just]

1010
01:02:02,760 --> 01:02:04,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: moving on after.]

1011
01:02:04,520 --> 01:02:06,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'll never know.]

1012
01:02:06,320 --> 01:02:09,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But if I start to
fixate on it and doubt things,]

1013
01:02:09,520 --> 01:02:12,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: there'll be no end to it.
So I tried not to think too much.]

1014
01:02:14,560 --> 01:02:16,560
[Cho Yun Jae:
It's time for the phone calls.]

1015
01:02:16,760 --> 01:02:18,640
[Oh Min Seong: What if he doesn't call me?]

1016
01:02:18,800 --> 01:02:21,520
[Taichi: Can I not make a call?]

1017
01:02:21,720 --> 01:02:24,840
[Cho Yun Jae:
What if I don't get any calls?]

1018
01:02:24,840 --> 01:02:26,960
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Just have to accept it. No other choice.]

1019
01:02:26,960 --> 01:02:29,560
[Cho Yun Jae:
I don't want to make a Plan B.]

1020
01:02:29,840 --> 01:02:31,600
[The trajectories of affection are unclear]

1021
01:02:31,600 --> 01:02:34,080
[Oh Min Seong:
It's beyond interest. I like you.]

1022
01:02:34,200 --> 01:02:35,760
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
We should go on a date tomorrow.]

1023
01:02:36,600 --> 01:02:38,120
[Cho Yun Jae: It's so funny.]

1024
01:02:38,760 --> 01:02:40,960
[Kim Han Gyeol: Don't tell anyone else.]

1025
01:02:41,280 --> 01:02:44,240
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You're the only one
to call, so I called you.]

1026
01:02:45,000 --> 01:02:46,240
[Kim Sun Wook: Hello?]

1027
01:02:48,880 --> 01:02:52,560
[Cho Yun Jae:
I made up my mind to be more proactive.]

1028
01:02:52,560 --> 01:02:55,400
[Kim Sun Wook: I made the effort
to show him even more that I like him.]

1029
01:02:55,680 --> 01:02:57,600
[Lee Hyun Jun: I was really conflicted.]

1030
01:03:02,200 --> 01:03:06,560
[Lee Hyun Jun: It would've been better
if today's date was just us two.]

1031
01:03:07,400 --> 01:03:09,990
[Who does Hyun Jun's heart belong to?]
